English, Englisch:
Sry for my bad english :D

For the (dis-)advantages for every map look at the 2nd picture!


Contacttime: 
fast: 3.5 seconds
normal: 6 seconds

Spawns:

30 for Counter Terrorists
30 for Terrorists

happy Fragging :D
